original: Map made by Puklica & Cuniczek
zh_trans: 地图作者为Puklica & Cuniczek

original: Sponge builder has been picked up.
zh_trans: 海绵墙已被拾取

original: Mouse trap has been picked up.
zh_trans: 老鼠夹已被拾取

original: We'll have to roll down the toilet paper to safely climb down.
zh_trans: 我们必须等卫生纸降到地面才能安全的下去

original: Toilet paper has been rolled down. Fall back!
zh_trans: 卫生纸降到地面了，撤退！

original: Hold for 15 seconds.
zh_trans: 守住15秒

original: Resist for 30 seconds.
zh_trans: 守住30秒

original: Resist for 25 seconds.
zh_trans: 守住25秒

original: Hold here until the blue sponge drops, then get in the tub!
zh_trans: 守住这里直到蓝色海绵帮我们阻挡住僵尸，然后我们就可以去浴缸了

original: The path is blocked. Fall back!
zh_trans: 道路已被阻挡，撤退！

original: The Rubber Duck has been defeated.
zh_trans: 泥头车鸭鸭已被击败

original: You have won first level!
zh_trans: 我们通过了第一关

original: Resist until the wall breaks.
zh_trans: 守住这里直到后面墙面破碎

original: Fall back!
zh_trans: 道路被清空，撤退！

original: We have to clear the soap out of the way to be able to climb up.
zh_trans: 我们需要一些时间把肥皂移开才能撤退

original: The path has been cleared.
zh_trans: 肥皂被移开了，从梳子爬上去！

original: We'll have to jump outside and walk across the mirror.
zh_trans: 看来我们得从镜子上面通过这里了

original: Hold on for a few seconds.
zh_trans: 守住这里一段时间

original: We can use the hairdryer to reach the shelf!
zh_trans: 我们可以利用吹风机到达对面的平台上！

original: Seems like there is no way to escape.
zh_trans: 看起来我们似乎无路可退了

original: That's it! Break the shelf support.
zh_trans: 有办法了！击碎上面那个支架！

original: We are trapped! Resist!
zh_trans: 无路可退了！守住这里！

original: Fall back we can walk across the door.
zh_trans: 跳过去！我们可以沿着门上方离开这里

original: There is no way around.
zh_trans: 没有其他选择了！

original: We'll have to enter the boiler. Resist!
zh_trans: 我们必须进入这个净水器

original: We can enter through that hole! Fall back!
zh_trans: 我们可以从这个破损的缺口进去！撤退！

original: The sponge has been defeated! Run!
zh_trans: 海绵方块被击败了！快离开这！

original: Final doors are going to close in 30 seconds! Resist!
zh_trans: 最后的橱柜将会在30秒后关闭！守住这里！

original: Kill all zombies inside!
zh_trans: 杀死进来的僵尸！

original: You have won the map! Congratulations!
zh_trans: 我们通关了这张地图！祝贺！
